<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.182262>
    bibo:endPage "47" ;
    bibo:journal "Zootaxa" ;
    bibo:startPage "37" ;
    bibo:volume "1778" ;
    dc:creator "Fontoura, Paulo; Pilato, Giovanni; Lisi, Oscar" ;
    dc:date "2008" ;
    dc:title "New records of eutardigrades (Tardigrada) from Faial and Pico Islands, the Azores, with the description of two new species" ;
    fabio:hasPart <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.182263>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.182264> ;
    a fabio:JournalArticle .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.182263>
    dc:description "FIGURE 1. A – G, Macrobiotus almadai sp. nov. (holotype): A, bucco-pharyngeal apparatus; B and C, claws of the third pair of legs; D, claws of the hind legs; E, egg; F and G, details of the egg shell (arrow indicates the small teeth of the terminal disc). (Scale bar = 10 µm)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/182263/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.182264>
    dc:description "FIGURE 2. A and B, Macrobiotus hufelandi: A, bucco-pharyngeal apparatus; B, detail of the egg (Scale bar = 10 µm). C and D, Macrobiotus sandrae (paratype): C, bucco-pharyngeal apparatus; D, detail of the egg (Scale bar = 10 µm)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/182264/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

